'''Mieri Siikuol''', (Mary Seacole, baan Mary Jane Grant)<ref name=mixedfolks>{{cite web|url=http://www.mixedfolks.com/historical3.htm|title=Mixed Historical Figures|publisher=MixedFolks|date=2003|accessdate=30 March 2008}}</ref><ref name="TVU">{{cite web|url=http://www.maryseacole.com/maryseacole/pages/aboutmary.html|title=About Mary Seacole|author=Elizabeth Anionwu|publisher=[[Thames Valley University]]|date=2006<!-- Date now at bottom of first page... -->|accessdate=30 March 2008}}</ref> <!--23 November-->1805&nbsp;– 14 May 1881) wena [[Jumieka]]n uman a Skatish ah Afrikan disent uu eh-setop wah "British Otel" biyain di lain juurin di [[Kraimian Waar]], we shi eh-diskraib az "a mes-tiebl ah komfatebl kwaataz fi sik ah kanvalesent afisa," ah shi eh-provaid soko fi wuundid saabisman pah di baklfiil.<ref name="TVU"/> Shi eh-awaad postyuumos di [[Jumiekan Aada a Merit]] ina 1991. Ina 2004 shi eh-vuot di grietis blak Britn.<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/3475445.stm "Nurse named greatest black Briton"], BBC News, 10 February 2004.</ref>

Shi eh-akwaya nalij a oerbal medisn ina di [[Kiaribiyan]]. Wen di Kraimian Waar brokout, shi aplai tu di Waar Afis fi asis bot deh rifyuuz ar. Shi chrabl indipendantli ah setop ar otel ah asis baklfiil wuundid. Shi weh extriimli papiula mongx saabis poersonel uu riez moni fi ar wen shi fies destityuushan afta di waar.

Afta ar det, deh figat bout ar fi liklmuos a senchri, bot tide shi selibriet az wah uman uu soksesfuli kombat rieshal prejiudis.<ref>''Who's Who in British History'', p. 715.</ref> Ar bayagrafi, ''Wandaful Advencha a Mischris Siikuol ina Nof Lan'' (Wonderful Adventures of Mrs. Seacole in Many Lands, 1857), a wan a di hoerlies aatobayagrafi a wah mix-ries uman, alduo kuestian riez bout soh aspek a iakiuresi. Soh kritik kliem se dat fi Siikuol achiivmentdem eh-egzajariet fi palitikal riizn<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2255095/The-black-Florence-Nightingale-making-PC-myth-One-historian-explains-Mary-Seacoles-story-stood-up.html#ixzz2Gd0fsPUr "The black Florence Nightingale and the making of a PC myth: One historian explains how Mary Seacole's story never stood up"], Mail Online, 31 December 2012.</ref> ah plan fi irek wah statiu a ar a Sin Tamas Aspital, Landan, we diskraib ar az a "payanier noers",<ref>[http://www.guysandstthomas.nhs.uk/resources/about-us/plans/Mary-Seacole-designs.pdf Mary Seacole Memorial Statue Appeal.]</ref> jinariet nof kas-kas.<ref>Natasha McEnroe, [http://www.historytoday.com/blog/2012/09/beyond-rivalry-florence-nightingale-and-mary-seacole "Beyond the Rivalry: Florence Nightingale and Mary Seacole"], ''History Today'', 3 September 2012.</ref><ref>Lynn McDonald, [http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/jun/08/mary-seacole-statue-florence-nightingale-disservice "Comment is free: Statue of 'nurse' Mary Seacole will do Florence Nightingale a disservice"], ''The Guardian'', 8 June 2012.</ref> Foerda kanchrovoersi brokout ina di [[Yunaitid Kindom]] liet ina 2012 uoba ripuot a propuozal fi rimuuv ar frah di konchri Nashinal Korikiulom.<ref>[http://www.obv.org.uk/news-blogs/michael-gove-dumps-mary-seacole "Michael Gove dumps Mary Seacole"], OBV, 2 January 2013.</ref>

